de.tuhh.diss.harborstorage.sim

Interface StorageElement


  • public interface StorageElement
    This interface abstracts a storage element (i.e. a packet) which can be stored into the harbor storage. It provides methods to get information about the size, the ID, textual description and weight of the storage element.
    Author:
    Weigel
